high_descs: Turn right and go to the microwave

high_descs: Turn right, turn left at the door, turn left at the fridge, and walk up to the microwave.
Open the microwave door, pick up the apple to the right of the potato, close the door.
Turn right to face the sink.
Put the apple down in the sink to the left of the spatula, rinse off the apple, pick up the apple.
Turn left to face the microwave.
Open the microwave door, place the apple inside the microwave, close the door.
anns.task_desc: To rinse off an apple and put it in the microwave.
